  <brief_title>Educational Tools to Improve Beliefs About Pain and Reduce Pain-related Disability</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Different Educational Tools to Improve Beliefs About Pain and Reduce Pain-related Disability in Patients With Chronic Low Back Pain: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
